      <title>随着关税担忧加剧，欧洲企业盈利或将保持乐观</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-earnings-may-keep-mood-sweet-tariff-fears-grow-2025-01-24/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲企业将连续第三个季度实现利润增长，这可能有助于在政治和经济动荡以及对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税威胁的担忧下维持投资者对该地区的新热情。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-earnings-may-keep-mood-sweet-tariff-fears-grow-2025-01-24/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 06:06:59 GMT</pubDate>
